refresh

public static void refresh(TreeLogger logger,
                           ResourceOracleImpl first,
                           ResourceOracleImpl... rest)
Rescans the associated paths to recompute the available resources. TODO(conroy,scottb): This synchronization could be improved upon to allow disjoint sets of oracles to be refreshed simultaneously.

Parameters:
logger - status and error details are written here
first - At least one ResourceOracleImpl must be passed to refresh
rest - Callers may optionally pass several oracles

clear

public void clear()

Frees up all existing resources and transient internal state. All returned collections will be empty after this call until this ResourceOracle is refreshed.
